headline: Why Western Digital (WDC) Stock Is Up Today
summary: Shares of leading data storage manufacturer Western Digital (NASDAQ: WDC) jumped 6.6% in the afternoon session after positive analyst actions, including an upgrade to "Overweight" and a significant price target increase from Barclays. Barclays raised its price target on the company to $240 from $200, while keeping an "Overweight" rating.
